## Example Scenarios (Generic Walkthrough)

### Scenario 1: User says "Start refactoring the product details page"

```text
Phase 1 Gathering (AI Parallel Exec):
  - Plugin Sniff: Detected .cursor/rules/ecommerce-playbook.mdc, read paths & constraints
  - Past Convos: Searched "product details" → 4 related found
  - Related Docs: docs/design/product_page_design.md §2.1
  - Existing Rules: p1-frontend-components.mdc matched
  - Code Deps: src/components/Product/ modules
  - Recent Changes: git log relevant commits

Phase 2 Summary (AI Presents):
  → Structured summary, referencing design doc §2.1

Phase 3 Confirmation (Human Decision):
  → User confirms: "Do the core purchase button area first"

Phase 4a (Human Selection): Path A - Deep design needed
Phase 4b (State Transition): User: "A, let's discuss button states" → Conditional
Phase 4c (AI drives brainstorming, human drives discussion):
  → brainstorming discusses OutOfStock, Preorder, Normal states
  → Frontend detected → Auto-load frontend-design
  → User: "Plan is set" → brainstorming exit signal
  → AI: "Enter Path B?" → User: "Yes" → Enter 4c chain
  → Load p1-frontend-components.mdc and execute
```

### Scenario 2: User says "Continue last time's payment module debugging"

```text
Phase 1 Gathering (AI Parallel Exec):
  - Past Convos: Found last Stripe Webhook signature triage progress
  - Existing Rules: payment-security.mdc matched

Phase 2 Summary (AI Presents):
  → Last progress, pending items, test conclusions

Phase 3 Confirmation (Human Decision):
  → User confirms: "Continue from the signature 401 error"

Phase 4a (Human Selection): Path D - Debug/Troubleshoot
Phase 4b (State Transition): User: "D, check like last time" → Confirmed
Phase 4c (AI Autonomous Execution):
  → Load payment-security.mdc
  → systematic-debugging (4 phases)
  → verification-before-completion
  → Report test conclusions
```

### Scenario 3: User says "Add a report export feature"

```text
Phase 1-3 (Human Driven):
  → Gather data structure docs, existing report code
  → User confirms requirements and constraints

Phase 4a (Human Selection): Path B - Clear plan, need execution
Phase 4b (State Transition): User: "B, go" → Confirmed
Phase 4c (AI Autonomous Chain):
  → writing-plans breaks it into 8 bite-sized tasks
  → test-driven-development writes generation logic tests first
  → subagent-driven-development executes in parallel
  → requesting-code-review after every 3 tasks
  → verification-before-completion for the whole suite
  → finishing-a-development-branch commits/PRs
```